(1)
3417 Ave. M, at the N.w. corner of East 35th Street, at Kings Higway, showing the John L. Ryder House, built about 1850 and occupied by
hiw from 1850 to 1873.
April 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(2)
The same, from another angle.
April 1923.
EVgene L. Armbruster Collection.
(3)
The same, from a distance on Kings Highway. The white house at
the left, is the Ryder House.
August 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
